nt\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The public's reaction reflects a growing unease about the rapid integration of AI into various aspects of life.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The public's reaction\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"a growing unease\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"the rapid integration\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"various aspects\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3658}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many are questioning whether this relentless push for AI adoption is coming at the cost of authentic human experiences, creativity, and expression.\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3722, \"end\": 3724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this relentless push\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3755}, {\"ngram\": \"authentic human experiences\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The concern extends beyond just creative endeavours.\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The concern\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"just creative endeavours\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is widespread speculation and anxiety about how artificial intelligence might reshape the job market across various industries.\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 4003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"widespread speculation\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"artificial intelligence\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3947}, {\"ngram\": \"the job market\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3976}, {\"ngram\": \"various industries\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 4002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Will AI replace human workers in certain fields?\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AI\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"human workers\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4033}, {\"ngram\": \"certain fields\", \"from\": 4037, \"to\": 4051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How will it change the nature of work?\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These ads, whether intentionally or not, seem to have touched a nerve, adding fuel to the fire of these existing anxieties.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These ads\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4101}, {\"ngram\": \"a nerve\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4161}, {\"ngram\": \"fuel\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"the fire\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4186}, {\"ngram\": \"these existing anxieties\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In light of these controversies, industry experts have weighed in on the debate, offering their perspectives on the ads and their implications.\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4225}, {\"ngram\": \"these controversies\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4248}, {\"ngram\": \"industry experts\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4266}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4296}, {\"ngram\": \"their perspectives\", \"from\": 4307, \"to\": 4325}, {\"ngram\": \"the ads\", \"from\": 4329, \"to\": 4336}, {\"ngram\": \"their implications\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naresh Gupta, co-founder at Bang in the Middle, a creative agency, offers a critical view of Google's Olympic ad, saying, \\\"Brands and advertisers live in a bubble, they live in their own world.\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4361, \"end\": 4367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allari_Naresh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0100579588422765e-31, \"text\": \"Naresh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allari_Naresh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allari_Naresh\"}, {\"begin\": 4368, \"end\": 4373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9999985326878083, \"rank\": 1.4668220432947307e-06, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}, {\"begin\": 4454, \"end\": 4460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4377}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4385}, {\"ngram\": \"Bang\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4393}, {\"ngram\": \"the Middle\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"a creative agency\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4426}, {\"ngram\": \"a critical view\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4450}, {\"ngram\": \"Brands\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4490}, {\"ngram\": \"advertisers\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4506}, {\"ngram\": \"a bubble\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4523}, {\"ngram\": \"their own world\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Disconnected from reality and only see what they want to see.\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 4573, \"to\": 4580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Google, search and data is the only way to look at the world and this is what we see in this ad.\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4621, \"end\": 4627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 4629, \"to\": 4635}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"the only way\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4660}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4681}, {\"ngram\": \"this ad\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so shocking to see human endeavour, perseverance, desire for excellence and scaling new peaks being reduced to an AI generated letter, only because Google wants to sell its wares.\\\"\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4837, \"end\": 4839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 4871, \"end\": 4877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"human endeavour\", \"from\": 4742, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4771}, {\"ngram\": \"desire\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4779}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4794}, {\"ngram\": \"new peaks\", \"from\": 4807, \"to\": 4816}, {\"ngram\": \"its wares\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naresh Gupta Gupta further elaborates on what he believes should be the proper role of AI, suggesting, \\\"AI is a tool.\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 5023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4912, \"end\": 4917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9999985326878083, \"rank\": 1.4668220432947307e-06, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}, {\"begin\": 4919, \"end\": 4924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9999985326878083, \"rank\": 1.4668220432947307e-06, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}, {\"begin\": 4993, \"end\": 4995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the proper role\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"AI\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5011}, {\"ngram\": \"a tool\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can help you get better.\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can help you craft something nice when you want a nudge.\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5074, \"to\": 5083}, {\"ngram\": \"a nudge\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Humanity cannot be driven robotically, the whole point of an 'assistant' is to have assistance.\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Humanity\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole point\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5166}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'assistant\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"assistance\", \"from\": 5196, \"to\": 5206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ideally, Google should have partnered father and Gemini to arrive at the wishes for her daughter.\\\"\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5217, \"end\": 5223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 5257, \"end\": 5263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9999999983938324, \"rank\": 1.6064865438058718e-09, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"father\", \"from\": 5246, \"to\": 5252}, {\"ngram\": \"the wishes\", \"from\": 5277, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"her daughter\", \"from\": 5292, \"to\": 5304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, not all industry voices are critical of the commercial.\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not all industry voices\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5340}, {\"ngram\": \"the commercial\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vikash Chemjong, CCO at Cheil India, offers a more nuanced view, highlighting some positive aspects of the Google ad.\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5390, \"end\": 5393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_creative_officer\", \"score\": 0.9999921127393462, \"rank\": 7.875996774514426e-06, \"text\": \"CCO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_creative_officer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_creative_officer\"}, {\"begin\": 5403, \"end\": 5408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.99964431761244, \"rank\": 0.00034295605664708676, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 5480, \"end\": 5486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vikash Chemjong\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5388}, {\"ngram\": \"a more nuanced view\", \"from\": 5417, \"to\": 5436}, {\"ngram\": \"some positive aspects\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He argues, \\\"There are so many positive things to it - the father daughter love.\", \"from\": 5491, \"to\": 5570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many positive things\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sporty daughter.\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sporty daughter\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her focus and determination.\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her focus\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5601}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 5606, \"to\": 5619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The father's effort to egg her on.\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The father's effort\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, it's warm and emotional.\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the so many things that are right for the film some have still managed to find a wrong!\\\"\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the so many things\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5713}, {\"ngram\": \"the film\", \"from\": 5733, \"to\": 5741}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrong\", \"from\": 5774, \"to\": 5781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vikas Chemjong Chemjong also questions the basis of the backlash, drawing parallels with other technological advancements, \\\"When you show people using a washing machine to wash clothes, I am not sure how it undermines the ability of humans to wash clothes.\", \"from\": 5785, \"to\": 6042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5785, \"end\": 5790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vikas_(rocket_engine)\", \"score\": 0.7980049875309648, \"rank\": 0.2531249999999833, \"text\": \"Vikas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vikas_(rocket_engine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vikas_(rocket_engine)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the basis\", \"from\": 5824, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 5837, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"parallels\", \"from\": 5859, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"other technological advancements\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 5906}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5923, \"to\": 5929}, {\"ngram\": \"a washing machine\", \"from\": 5936, \"to\": 5953}, {\"ngram\": \"clothes\", \"from\": 5962, \"to\": 5969}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 6003, \"to\": 6014}, {\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 6018, \"to\": 6024}, {\"ngram\": \"clothes\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or their ability to reach from point A to B when we advertise a bike.\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Or their ability\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6059}, {\"ngram\": \"point\", \"from\": 6074, \"to\": 6079}, {\"ngram\": \"B\", \"from\": 6085, \"to\": 6086}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 6105, \"to\": 6111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought the point of technology was that it helps us do things better, faster, easier.\\\"\", \"from\": 6113, \"to\": 6202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6132}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 6136, \"to\": 6146}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6165, \"to\": 6167}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 6171, \"to\": 6177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the controversy continues to unfold, Google has inadvertently found itself in the midst of a significant communications crisis.\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6244, \"end\": 6250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 6207, \"to\": 6222}, {\"ngram\": \"the midst\", \"from\": 6285, \"to\": 6294}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant communications crisis\", \"from\": 6298, \"to\": 6333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tech giant, known for its innovative approach to marketing, is now at the mercy of its public relations team as it grapples with the backlash.\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tech giant\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6349}, {\"ngram\": \"its innovative approach\", \"from\": 6361, \"to\": 6384}, {\"ngram\": \"marketing\", \"from\": 6388, \"to\": 6397}, {\"ngram\": \"the mercy\", \"from\": 6409, \"to\": 6418}, {\"ngram\": \"its public relations team\", \"from\": 6422, \"to\": 6447}, {\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 6468, \"to\": 6480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This situation raises important questions about crisis management in the age of social media: How can a brand recuperate from such a situation?\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This situation\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6496}, {\"ngram\": \"important questions\", \"from\": 6504, \"to\": 6523}, {\"ngram\": \"crisis management\", \"from\": 6530, \"to\": 6547}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 6551, \"to\": 6558}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 6562, \"to\": 6574}, {\"ngram\": \"such a situation\", \"from\": 6608, \"to\": 6624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What are the right steps to take to minimise the damage and rebuild trust with consumers?\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right steps\", \"from\": 6635, \"to\": 6650}, {\"ngram\": \"the damage\", \"from\": 6671, \"to\": 6681}, {\"ngram\": \"trust\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6699}, {\"ngram\": \"consumers\", \"from\": 6705, \"to\": 6714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarunjeet Rattan, managing partner at Nucleus PR, offers insights into how the company might navigate these turbulent waters.\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6755, \"end\": 6762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeping\", \"score\": 0.9999995645376696, \"rank\": 4.345493868205197e-07, \"text\": \"Nucleus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeping\"}, {\"begin\": 6763, \"end\": 6765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.672302355289454e-30, \"text\": \"PR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarunjeet Rattan\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6733}, {\"ngram\": \"managing partner\", \"from\": 6735, \"to\": 6751}, {\"ng